title: I AM ATHLETE: FAT JOE |  I'M UNDERRATED AND OVERLOOKED
description:
I AM ATHLETE Miami | Season 3: Episode 15

Brandon Marshall, Chad Johnson, D.J. Williams and LeSean McCoy welcome American rapper Fat Joe in episode 15  I AM ATHLETE Miami. 

Fat Joe discuss everything from how he changed the music landscape by discovering superstars like Big Pun and how he ended his beef with Jay Z. 

The group come together to drop a bombshell on aspiring entrepreneur Chef Starr-- pledging to fund her dreams of becoming the next big thing in the Miami food scene. 

Fat Joe also explains how he was integral in reviving the Rucker Park basketball scene and gives the real reason he agreed to battle Ja Rule in that epic Verzuz showdown.
